{
  "stem": "8834.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And the fact is, after the war finished, people who were together with my camp in-- with me, they came up to me and said, thanks to you, I'm alive.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And that was a very good feeling.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And it still is.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They know me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I have witnesses-- tens of them here in Toronto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And they know-- all of them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And my sisters were the same.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "My sister Bella was the youngest kommandanten in camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But how she-- what she did for people was unbelievable in such conditions where we were.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And she was beaten by a-- by a meister because she didn't-- she didn't say to the workers to do the job as they did.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "She picked up the-- the-- the-- the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I don't-- [LAUGHS] --she picked up the-- the ammunition from the floor.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "What-- when they work on the machine, they fall down sometimes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And this was [NON-ENGLISH], doing [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "This is a-- this is a terrible thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "So she did it for-- for them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "She couldn't there by all the people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And she-- and she couldn't meister with them to do this or do that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "So she was beaten for that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They did very bad thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First of all, this was a terrible thing to sell-- to sell their food.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And people were starving.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They looked like [NON-ENGLISH], like Muselmanns, they called them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were selling people's shoe-- people's life!",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was one of things.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then they took money for doing favors to them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Favors?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When one-- one was feeling bad, to stay in the barracks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was no good too, because there was-- they came.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And a-- and a company from the German see who was in the barrack.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And if you were sick, you are no good to work.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
